13 U.S. 🇺🇸 service members will be riding with me tomorrow — 10 of those from nearby Camp Pendleton. I'm incredibly thankful for our heroes who have fought and continue to fight for our great nation and I’ll never forget their sacrifice 🙏🏼

@alpinestars @alpinestarsmx
